| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0662 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c5bdeaf8-54c2-5af6-b734-93ae8c1f4398"
